{{For|the mythical blade|Flaming sword (mythology)}}
{{unreferenced|date=December 2008}}
[[Image:Fire Swords Performer with Flaming Swords - Dan Miethke.jpg|thumb|right|300px|A fire swords performer]]

A '''flaming sword''' is a [[sword]] that has been coated with some type of [[combustion|combustible]] [[fuel]], with the fuel being set on [[fire]]. This is most widely done for entertainment purposes in [[circuses]], [[Magic (illusion)|magic]] performances and other forms of display as a side act of [[sword swallowers]], [[fire eating]], etc.

