en Ohne Auto|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20040818083143/http://www.wohnen-ohne-auto.de/projekte.htm|archivedate=August 18, 2004|language=German}}</ref> |- |[[Münster]] (Geist) Gartensiedlung Weissenburg || || 184 dwellings || New development (2001)<ref>{{cite web|title=The car-free settlement Weißenburg in Münster|url=http://www.gartensiedlung-weissenburg.de/umwelt/die-autofreie-siedlung-weisenburg-in-munster/|website=Gartensiedlung|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120505162416/http://www.gartensiedlung-weissenburg.de/umwelt/die-autofreie-siedlung-weisenburg-in-munster/|archivedate=May 5, 2012|language=German|date=October 14, 2011}}</ref> |}
