== North America ==
=== Canada === ''NB'': Much of Canada's near north (the [[subarctic]] or [[boreal forest (Canada)|boreal forest]]) and virtually all of the area north of the [[tree line]] is [[trackless]], containing no roads. However, there are few large settlements in this area. In the towns and villages which do exist, motorized vehicles, in the form of [[All-terrain vehicle|ATVs]] and [[snowmobiles]] are commonplace. There are also isolated fishing villages on the North Atlantic coast called [[Newfoundland outports]] which are mostly car-free. {{further information|remote and isolated community}}
