'''Sandsinkers''' are [[lead (element)|lead]]-free fishing [[Sinker (fishing)|sinker]]s made of fabric and filled with sand. Although they do not [[casting (fishing)|cast]] as easily or as far for [[surf fishing]], they are a healthy alternative to lead for fishing from [[jetty|jetties]] or any situation where casting distance is not a prime consideration.

